div.p:
Thirty deaths from cattle plague have been notified in Egypt during the
                            week ending 8th inst. These cases have occurred in the following
                            districts :— Belbeis, 1 ;
                                Hehia, 3 ;
                                Shibin-el-Kom, 20 ;
                                Menouf, 1, and Beni
                                Souef, 1. The number of deaths daring the corresponding
                            period last year was 1,156. Since the commencement of the epidemic the
                            total number of deaths amounts to 147,321, distributed as follows
                            :—Gouvernorats, 892, Lower Egypt, 54,193 ; Upper Egypt, 92,236.
